  "body": "Related to this: https://github.com/ConsenSys/doc.teku/pull/421/files\n\nWe haven't really run any tests to determine the minimum/recommended system requirements for Teku.\n\nWe should have the following:\n\n- Minimum/Recommended system requirements for Mainnet beacon node (no validators)\n- Some guidance on how to scale up the system requirements when adding validators (e.g. for X validators, a minimum of 4 CPU cores, etc). Probably a bit guesswork but at least enough to help users.\n- Some example configurations based on our current production machines.",
